---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The coursework, explained" active="task">
  <div class="part-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">The assessment</p>
      <h1>The coursework, explained</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="band">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p>One piece of imaginative writing for the Edexcel International GCSE English Language coursework, drafted over weeks. Marks reward imaginative engagement with form and audience and the technical control of structure, sentences, spelling and punctuation. Because this is assessed coursework, the piece must be entirely the student's own work and AI must not write or edit any of it, so there is no AI feedback tool on this site. Craft guides, worked examples and the drafting timeline will appear here as the unit is taught.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
